import React from 'react' import { UilArrowDown, UilArrowUp, UilSun, UilWind, UilTear, UilSunset, UilTemperature, } from "@iconscout/react-unicons"; import { formatToLocalTime, iconURLFromCode } from '../services/weatherService'; function TempDetails({weather: {feels_like, humidity, temp, temp_max, temp_min, sunrise, sunset, details, icon, speed}}) { return (

{`${temp.toFixed()}°`}

Feels like: {`${feels_like.toFixed()}°`}
Humidity: {`${humidity.toFixed()}%`}
Wind: {`${speed.toFixed()} km/h`}

Rise: {formatToLocalTime(sunrise, "hh:mm a")}

|

Set: {formatToLocalTime(sunset, "hh:mm a")}

|

High: {`${temp_max.toFixed()}°`}

|

Low: {`${temp_min.toFixed()}°`}

|

) } export default TempDetails
